# ECIS Page Templates & Layout Patterns

## Template Hierarchy Rules
**DO NOT invent new sections.** Follow these exact page structures:

## 1. Home Page Template ([src/views/Home.vue](mdc:src/views/Home.vue))
Required sections in order:
```vue
<template>
  <Navigation />
  
  <!-- 1. Hero Section -->
  <HeroSection>
    <!-- Headline + Supporting line + Primary CTA + Secondary CTA + Trust badges -->
  </HeroSection>
  
  <!-- 2. Proof/Stats Section -->
  <section class="proof-section">
    <!-- 3-4 stats in badge cards: Years experience, Response time, Properties protected, Client satisfaction -->
  </section>
  
  <!-- 3. Services Preview -->
  <ServicesSection>
    <!-- 3-6 service cards: Patrol, HOA Security, Investigations, CCTV, Training -->
  </ServicesSection>
  
  <!-- 4. Technology Section -->
  <section class="technology-section">
    <!-- GPS tracking, Real-time reporting, CCTV monitoring, Mobile apps -->
