## Page-Specific Component Rules

### Navigation Component ([src/components/Navigation.vue](mdc:src/components/Navigation.vue))
- Fixed position with scroll-triggered background
- Mobile hamburger menu with accessibility features
- Active page indication with underline
- Logo on left, menu items center/right

