- Contact information (phone, email, address)
- Quick links to main pages
- Social media links
- Copyright and licensing information
- Emergency phone number prominence

## Quality Gates for Page Templates
Before shipping any page:
- [ ] Follows exact template structure (no invented sections)
- [ ] Hero section includes all required elements
- [ ] CTA buttons use action-oriented text
- [ ] Contact information is prominently displayed
- [ ] Mobile responsive at all breakpoints
- [ ] Loading states for dynamic content
- [ ] SEO meta tags properly set